# IP Lookup Tool

This is a simple web-based application that allows users to search for IP address information including location, country, and ISP. It also displays the geographical location on a map.

## Features

- Get IP address information (City, Country, ISP)
- Google Maps integration for location display
- Copy IP button for quick copy
- Toggle between Light and Dark themes

## How to Use

1. Open the app in your browser.
2. Enter an IP address in the input field.
3. Click on **Lookup** to fetch the data.
4. Click **Copy IP** to copy the result.
5. Use **Toggle Theme** to switch between dark/light mode.

## Live Preview

You can host the `index.html` on any static site service (GitHub Pages, Netlify, Vercel) or open it directly in your browser.

## API Used

Data is fetched from [ipapi.co](https://ipapi.co/).

